      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty car and it's looking for a great new home! It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. I've taken great care of it, so it's clean, comfy, and ready for all your upcoming road trips. It drives like a dream and honestly looks fantastic in person. Come swing by and take it for a spin\u2014I think you're really going to love how it feels on the road!",
      "price": 31500.0,
