    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the iconic S54B32 inline-six, renowned for its high-pressure VANOS system and individual throttle bodies. The powertrain is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, delivering linear power to a variable M differential lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe to address common chassis fatigue. The suspension has been refreshed with Bilstein dampers and polyurethane bushings, preserving the original kinematic precision. While the exterior shows minor stone chipping consistent with use, the mechanical integrity is exceptional, offering a visceral 8,000 RPM redline experience for the true purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
