    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of pride in ownership, offering a seamless blend of performance and comfort. The exterior retains a beautiful, high-gloss finish, showing only the slightest signs of careful use, such as minor stone chips typical of highway driving. Inside, the interior is exceptionally clean; the seats are supportive and free of any significant wear or staining, and the cabin has been kept strictly smoke-free. Every electronic feature, from the premium audio system to the intuitive navigation and heated seats, operates perfectly. Under the hood, the engine is clean and responsive, benefiting from a documented history of routine oil changes and preventative maintenance. The transmission shifts smoothly through all gears, and the suspension remains tight and quiet over bumps. With plenty of life left on the tires and brakes, this car is ready for immediate enjoyment with no hidden surprises. It represents a fantastic opportunity to own a high-quality vehicle that has been treated with respect.",
      "price": 34500.0,
